caption.text:
Create your personal brand in 30 seconds⬇️

1. Learn to edit ✍️ 

Premiere Pro is what I use, but equally you can use capcut, davinci etc…

2. Develop your style 🎨

Fonts, transitions, camera styles, colour palette etc. This is essential for building a recognisable brand.

3. Create Quality Content 📲

Focus on quality, people want to watch visually appealing content, take time with it, post content that you’re proud of…

4. Stick to your content strategy🤞

There is an art to content: attract, nurture, qualify, sell. Follow my YouTube for a better explaination.

5. Stay consistent😎

I posted twice a day for 5 week and gained 300 followers.
In the last week I’ve gained 7000.

6. Monetise🎱

There are a few ways to do this, again, I’ll go over my favourites on YouTube and inside my innerr circle, CreatorX.

Comment ‘X’ to join the content mentorship (only 10 spots, be quick)🗺️
